<h3 class="bar color">Avoiding scam and fraud attempts</h3>
 <div class="container gray">
<ul>
<br />
<li style="margin-left:1em">Never give out personal financial information. Beware of phony business 
calls and emails.</li>
<li style="margin-left:1em">Stop international fraud. Deal locally whenever possible.</li>
<li style="margin-left:1em">Watch for buyers who offer more than your asking price and who ask to 
have money wired or handed to them. Fake cashier checks and
money orders are common.</li>
<li style="margin-left:1em">Trust your instincts. Be wary of someone using an escrow service or agent 
to pick up merchandise or conduct other transactions you have advertised.</li>
</ul>
</div>

<li style="margin-left:1em">Something just doesn't feel right.</li>

function toggleValue(classVal, idVal) {
    jQuery('.'+classVal).toggle();
    if (document.getElementById(idVal).value == '0') { document.getElementById(idVal).value='1'; } else { document.getElementById(idVal).value='0'; }    
}
function hideClass(classVal) {
    jQuery('.'+classVal).hide();
}    
function showClass(classVal) {
    jQuery('.'+classVal).show();
}
function checkState () {
    if (document.getElementById('TOK').value == 0) { hideClass('iC_TOK1'); }    
    if (document.getElementById('TLC').value == 0) { hideClass('iC_TLC3'); }    
}    
function checkAll () {
    if (document.getElementById('TOK').value == 0) { hideClass('iC_TOK1'); }    
    if (document.getElementById('ADG').value == 0) { hideClass('iC_ADG2'); }    
    if (document.getElementById('TLC').value == 0) { hideClass('iC_TLC3'); }    
    if (document.getElementById('DMN').value == 0) { hideClass('iC_DMN5'); }    
    if (document.getElementById('TCA').value == 0) { hideClass('iC_TCA6'); }    
}

    		<b>Five-Year Review for the</b> <b>Mosley Road Sanitary Landfill</b> <b>Superfund Site</b> The Oklahoma Department of Environmental Quality (DEQ) and the U.S. Environmental Protection Agency (EPA) are beginning the five-year review of the Mosley Road Sanitary Landfill Superfund Site in August 2013. The purpose of this review is to determine whether the site remedy remains protective of human health and the environment and to document the methods, findings, and conclusions of the fiveyear review in a report. The report will be available to the public in May 2014. This will be the fourth Five-Year Review for the site. The site is located between N.E. 23rd and N.E. 36th Streets at 3300 Mosley Road in Oklahoma City, OK. The landfill received hazardous waste between February 1976 and August 1976. The remedy selected in the June 1992 Record of Decision addressed the source and contaminated ground water at the site. The remedy included repair and improvement of the existing cap and ground water and landfill gas monitoring. If you have any questions or need further information about the five-year review please contact Amber Brawdy, DEQ, Environmental Programs Specialist, Land Protection Division, Site Remediation Section (405) 702-5133 or Michael Torres, EPA, Region 6, Remedial Project Manager (214) 789-9751.     		<b>LOIS A. THOMAS</b> <b>Sept 24, 1918 - Aug 22, 2007</b> Dearest Mother, Another year has flown by with hardly a day that we don't think of you - and Dad - with both a deep sense of loss and gratitude, gratitude for so much that you imparted to not only your family (husband Virgil of over 60 years, five children and 17 grandchildren) but innumerable students, friends and beneficiaries of your decades of generosity and service. You left us a wonderful legacy of "leading by example": such as Oklahoma Medical Research Foundation, which has received millions (over the past 30 years) as the result of your initial campaign to raise funds at Putnam City Schools for cancer research. One of life's most noble professions is that of being a teacher, a steward entrusted with the minds of young people. For over 30 years, you discharged your calling with dedication and passion. The lives forever changed are too numerous to recall, but existing and future generations will have a better quality of life because of your investment of time and talent in them. We were scarcely more proud than when annually, at the University of Oklahoma, you bestowed the "Lois A. Thomas Journalism Award" upon the outstanding journalism teacher in the State of Oklahoma. Other notable examples are: your years of assistance to Christian icon A. W. Tozer of Chicago; classmate of Evangelist Billy Graham and wife Ruth at Wheaton College; candidate for Mrs. America (of which we were enormously proud); earning a Master's Degree while diligently serving as wife, mother and teacher; becoming an accomplished musician; having a heart for missions since childhood and years of service with Dad in the Gideons and so much more. We love you, Mother, and miss you deeply. Above all, your family is forever grateful for the Christian heritage that you and Dad imbued in us, resultantly our own children and yes, even generations yet unborn. This heritage of salvation, grace and forgiveness has given us all the certainty of eternity with our Lord and Savior, Jesus Christ, you, Dad and a host of family and friends. We're thankful for your and Dad's influence and commitment to God's Word by faithfully raising your children "in the nurture and admonition of the Lord." Looking forward with great anticipation to seeing you again, we remain, Your Devoted Family

                                                    <script>
	function printCoupon(elem) {
		Popup($(elem).html());
	}
	function Popup(data) {
		var mywindow = window.open('', '', 'width=500,height=740');
		mywindow.document.write('<html><head><title>NewsOK Classifieds | Print</title>');
		mywindow.document.write('<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="http://s3.amazonaws.com/content.newsok.com/newsok/css/classifieds/classifieds2009b.css" />');
		mywindow.document.write('<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" media="print" href="http://s3.amazonaws.com/content.newsok.com/newsok/css/classifieds/classifieds-print-2013.css" />');
		mywindow.document.write('</head><body>');
		mywindow.document.write(data);
		mywindow.document.write('</body></html>');
		mywindow.document.close();
		mywindow.focus();
		mywindow.print();
		mywindow.close();
		return true;
	}
</script>
<script>
	(function($) {
		$(document).ready(function() {
			$('a.tab').each(function() {
				var attr = $(this).attr('onclick');
				if ((typeof attr !== 'undefined' && attr !== false) && $(this).attr('onclick') == 'window.print();return false;') {
					$(this).removeAttr('onclick').click(function(e) {
						e.preventDefault();
						var toBePrinted = $('.classifiedsColumn');
						printCoupon(toBePrinted);
					});
				}
			});
		});
	})(jQuery);
</script>

            <script>
                var hideSub;
                var showSub;
                var thisSub = "classifieds_Local,recreation-off-road-vehicles-and-atvs"; 
                
                $(document).ready(function() {
                    $('.openSubNav').mouseover(function() {
                        if ($('.subSubnavWrapper').css('height') == '65px') {
                            $('.subSubnav').hide();
                            $('#subSubnav_'+this.id).show();
                        } else {
                            $('.subSubnav').hide();
                            $('#subSubnav_'+this.id).show();
                            $('.subSubnavWrapper').css('height', '65px');
                            $('#mainBody').addClass('subnav');
                            setTimeout("$('.subSubnavWrapper').css('overflow', 'visible');", 750);
                        }
                    });
                    $(document).ready(function() {
                        $('#subNav').bind("mouseleave",function() {
                            hideSub=setTimeout("hideSubNav()", 2000);
                            showSub=setTimeout("$('#subSubnav_'+thisSub).show()", 2000);
                        });
                        $('#subNav').bind("mouseenter",function() {
                            clearTimeout(hideSub);
                            clearTimeout(showSub);
                        });
                    });
                    // search box
                    var searchImg = $('.search-icon img').attr('src');
                    $('.search-icon').click(function(e) {
                        e.preventDefault();
                        if ($(this).find('img').attr('src') == searchImg) {
                            $(this).toggleClass('active').find('img').attr('src', 'http://s3.amazonaws.com/content.newsok.com/newsok/refactor/icon_search_close.png').parent().next().toggleClass('hide');
                        } else {
                            $(this).toggleClass('active').find('img').attr('src', searchImg).parent().next().toggleClass('hide');
                        }
                    });
                });
                function hideSubNav() {
                    if(document.getElementById('subSubnav_'+thisSub) == null) {
                        $('.subSubnavWrapper').css('overflow', 'hidden');
                        $('#mainBody').removeClass('subnav');
                        $('.subSubnavWrapper').css('height', '0px');
                    }
                }
                if (document.getElementById('subSubnav_'+thisSub) != null) {
                    $('.subSubnav').css('height', '0px');
                    $('.subSubnavWrapper').css('height', '65px');
                    $('#subSubnav_'+thisSub).css('height', '65px');
                    $('#mainBody').addClass('subnav');
                }
                
            </script>
            
            <script>
                
                offsetPos = document.getElementById('subNav').offsetTop;
                $('#subNav').affix({offset: offsetPos});
                
            </script>
